# Global styles

- Keep design tokens in `:root` inside `styles/styles.css`
- Do not load external font CDNs; use self-hosted `fonts/`
- Put non-critical rules in `lazy-styles.css`
- Preserve LCP-friendly loading (fonts after first paint)
- Section utility classes: `.surface`, `.pixel-divider`, `.accent-border`, `.dark`
